data.description: Discover your next home -- this fantastic house is ready for new owners, offering a spacious primary bedroom with a walk-in closet for your convenience. Step outside to a serene setting enveloped by mature trees, creating a natural oasis in your backyard. Located equidistant between the Bulverde/Spring Branch City Center and the beauty of Canyon Lake, this neighborhood perfectly balances country and city living. Enjoy an array of Hill Country neighborhood amenities, including a fishing pond, river access, a swimming pool, walking trails, nature areas, tennis/pickleball courts, and even camping grounds. This is the lifestyle you've been searching for. Don't wait; come take a look today and make this home yours!
